Description: Fragmen t of neck and oval handle to moderate turn of a Pamphylian pottery transport amphora. Clay near fine medium brown. Rectangular stamp.
Curator's comments: As. C. Brixhe, Timbres amphoriques de Pamphylie (Paris, 2012) nos 149-154.
Bibliographic references: Stoddart 1847 / Memoir on the inscribed pottery of Rhodes, Cnidus and other Greek Cities (342)
